metadata.name: A Lonely Walk
metadata.description:
The world feels so big, doesn’t it?

We’re all scared and that’s okay. 
The world is going through a tough time, I know.  
Please, have a walk. Loneliness is just part of being human, because you are trying to remember who you truly are. No matter if you’re a loner or have the fear of being alone, just remind yourself that you’re never really alone. An ode to everyone going through a hard time. 

This is ‘A Lonely Walk’ : a unique topdown street view shot by yours truly.

Artist: Naty  
Name: A Lonely Walk 
Edition: 20/20  
Location: Milan, Italy  
Year: 2022  
Size: 4834 x 7248  
Gear: Sony a7RIII - Sony 85mm F1.8 
Genre: Street Photography
